(What's Unitron's status...?)

Shockwave:



Shockwave checked his internal chronometer and with the disappearance of Hell 
Beast's Predacon forces he was drastically off track, which was not like him.

He looked to Megatron.  "Megatorn," he intoned, "I must return to my base.  
Urgent plans are already off course and must be repaired.  We will discuss 
matters later.  I trust you will send my officer back after he is finished 
with his repairs?" Shockwave asked, his single optic 'blinking' with each 
word.
